  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior WSH Executive (Logistics MNC)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a well-established MNC, market leader in the 3PL Logistics industry. Due to their current expansion plan, they are looking for Senior WSH Executive to join their HSSE team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located in the East - easily accessible.</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities Senior WSH Executive:</strong></p><ul><li>Monitor and enforce workplace safety practices across multiple sites</li><li>Investigate and report safety violations; initiate safety time-outs when required</li><li>Support incident prevention through regular site assessments and safety audits</li><li>Work closely with teams to ensure compliance with WSH regulations and ISO 45001 / 14001 standards</li><li>Travel across Singapore sites (up to 50%)</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>WSQ Specialist Diploma in WSH or Degree/Diploma in Occupational Health & Safety or related fields</li><li>Registered WSH Officer with MOM</li><li>At least 3 years of relevant HSE experience in corporate or industrial settings</li><li>Familiar with ISO 14001, ISO 45001, OSHA, and local regulatory requirements</li><li>Strong communication, stakeholder engagement, and problem-solving skills</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office; knowledge of Power BI, PowerApps, or RPA tools is an advantage</li><li>ISO Lead Auditor certification and NEBOSH/CSP/CIH/GRI preferred</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.<br /></p><p><strong>Email: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License No. 19C9682</p><p>EA Reg. No. R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
